      • fromFullString

        public static java.util.List<TypeInfo<?>> fromFullString(java.lang.String fullString)
        Parse fullString and returns TypeInfo list that fullString represents. This method will not resolve the types, it will provide them as class literal, to resolve and load types use: TypeInfo.loadTypes(Function). This method can parse TypeMirror type representation.
        Parameters:
        fullString - String representation of an TypeInfo.
        Returns:
        TypeInfo list that fullString represents.

      • fromFullString

        public static java.util.List<TypeInfo<?>> fromFullString(java.lang.String fullString,
                                                         java.util.function.Function<java.lang.String,java.lang.Class<?>> classResolver)
        Parse fullString and returns TypeInfo list that fullString represents. This method can resolve types through classResolver, if the resolver returns null, the class will not be resolved, the TypeInfo will be constructed with type literals that can be resolved later using TypeInfo.loadTypes(Function). This method can parse TypeMirror type representation.
        Parameters:
        fullString - String representation of an TypeInfo.
        classResolver - Resolver of string to class.
        Returns:
        TypeInfo list that fullString represents.
